{"tid":2202131,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(劇透) TENET 天能=> 天能能力是甚麼???(純粹討論能力相關資料)","createTime":"2020-09-14T10:46:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T17:58:34.000Z","uid":259520,"like":4,"dislike":109,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"1ba67320a2050700889e4716fde3bf63278e05a0","tid":2202131,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:46:40.000Z","msg":"(劇透) TENET 天能=&gt; 天能能力是甚麼???(純粹討論能力相關資料)<br />\n[有錯請指出]<br />\n天能=&gt; 係一種機器可以帶人或物回到過去. <br />\n但過程中人或會經過其他人物逆轉行為.<br />\n<br />\n只有有天能既人先可以看到,另一天能既人行動.<br />\n<br />\n子彈例子=&gt; <br />\n主角最初不能夠拿起子彈,因為主角認為粒子彈非在佢手中掉落.<br />\n科學家叫佢想像, 子彈之前係由佢手中掉落, 就可以拿起子彈.<br />\n<br />\n同樣佢以為槍有子彈,實際係無, 但當佢開槍就有子彈(子彈由想像產生)<br />\n由想像之前為真, 就可真實化.<br />\n<br />\n人在逆行中要用呼吸器,唔係就會缺氧而死.(有無其他資料??)"},{"pid":"8db52705594187f55ce19ef29626cd03bd23e451","tid":2202131,"uid":66893,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"其實你有冇睇過套戲架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0afc321fbe7476491c167a081a8d22c916459d","tid":2202131,"uid":31174,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:56:33.000Z","msg":"天能係個組織嚟架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪見到有個能字就係超能力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93b9cde69adccb0fad060a77666a2360d9fae4c","tid":2202131,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":33,"score":-33,"quote":{"pid":"8db52705594187f55ce19ef29626cd03bd23e451","tid":2202131,"uid":66893,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"其實你有冇睇過套戲架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"咁有咩野錯???<br />\n<br />\n無睇就唔會知子彈個幕!!"},{"pid":"571992380177384547cfbc6182d2c09368da493f","tid":2202131,"uid":259520,"like":1,"dislike":39,"score":-38,"quote":{"pid":"7d0afc321fbe74